item.title: Help! whats are some good item ids?
item.dc:creator: @nuradonai nuradonai
item.description:
@nuradonai wrote:

Download Moparscape. Open Moparscape30 folder. Open Hybridscape folder. Open all_ids folder. Now open items.xml with notepad and use ctrl+f to find any item your looking for.
